<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8345380>
    dc:description "FIGURES 124–132. Lomechusoides strumosus Fabricius, 1792. 124, male, dorsal habitus; 125, male, pronotum in dorsal view (L: 1.07 mm, W: 1.77 mm), (locality: Bohemia: Týn nad Vltavou); 126, male, microstructure of elytra with setation; 127, male, aedeagus, lateral view; 128, male, aedeagus, ventral view; 129, female, antennomeres IX–X, (locality: Bohemia: Týn nad Vltavou); 130, male, metaventral process; 131, male, apex of paramere; 132, female, spermatheca, (locality: Bohemia: Týn nad Vltavou). Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8345380/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8345374>
    dc:description "FIGURES 102–108. Lomechusoides rossii sp. nov. 102–107, male holotype. 102, dorsal habitus; 103, pronotum in dorsal view (L: 1.10 mm, W: 1.85 mm); 104, aedeagus, lateral view; 105, aedeagus, ventral view; 106, metaventral process; 107, apex of paramere; 108, female paratype, spermatheca. Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8345374/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

